choices.text:
### Human:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds
### Assistant:

Here is a sample meal plan that meets your dietary restrictions:

Breakfast: Oatmeal with fruit and nuts (without almonds)
Lunch: Grilled chicken breast with roasted vegetables and quinoa
Snack: Apple slices with peanut butter
Dinner: Baked salmon with sweet potato and green beans
